	('39ea6368-e864-4d81-b5a0-7d497520ac9d', 'Determine the techniques and technologies to address the identified requirements.', 10, '[0 - 2) - Failure to provide techniques and technologies to address identified requirements. ; [2 - 5) - Provide less than 40% of the techniques and technologies to address the identified requirements. ; [5 - 8) - Provide adequate techniques and technologies to address identified requirements.\r\n- Reasonably explain the reasons for choosing that technique and technology to solve the requirements. ; [8 - 10] - Provide adequate techniques and technologies to address identified requirements.\r\n- Reasonably explain the reasons for choosing that technique and technology to solve the requirements.\r\n- The techniques and technologies used to solve the identified requirements are new and follow future trends.', 'REVIEWER', '2024-08-19 16:17:21', '2024-08-19 16:17:21', '71e2da71-ddc1-4da6-aede-08cdd36b2eab'),
